title: Medieval Total War + Samurai warlords (directplay)
description:
Info about the mod here: http://www.die-hermetische-garage.de/Warlords.html

It's pretty much Shogun Total war with 24 clans and Medieval total war features. 
I removed most of the mtw files to get the size down, and it comes pre-cracked.

If you liked Shogun: total war, this is a must have.

NOTE : This is a modded copy of the game not the vanilla game!
